descriptionHtml:
She is located in The Bannered Mare in Whiterun she wanders around inside

Tali majors in Archery but will use a sword when enemies get to close to her
she comes with a Bow,999 Daedric arrow and a Elven longsword. She is wearing Full Elven armor except the helm. She has a Circlet with archery stats in it.

If you want the Armor from the second pic you will need Arise - Chapter 1 - The Black Sacrament by [b]AmethystDeceiver[/b] 



You will need 2 things for correct face and Hair 

Ethereal Elven Overhaul by nuska 
KS Hairdos - Renewal by [b]Kalilies Stealthic Khaos and Shocky[/b]
